welcome_message_body: "Welcome to Timberwood Park, where the charm of small-town America meets the excitement of a bustling city. Get ready to explore our beautiful parks, quaint shops, and delicious dining options. We hope you enjoy your stay and make unforgettable memories in our charming city."
